**/node_modules
**/dist
**/coverage
**/.next
**/*.test.ts
**/*.test.tsx
**/jest.config.*
**/tsconfig.json
.eslintrc*
.prettierrc*
playwright-report

# Infrastructure and deployment files
infrastructure/terraform
infrastructure/monitoring
docker-compose*.yml
.vercel

# Documentation and metadata files not needed in runtime
**/README.md
**/*.md
LICENSE